.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-RUNE-CREATE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-rune-create \- create a new access rune for the Lightning daemon
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-rune-create
.RI [ restriction ...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Calls
.B lightning-cli createrune
to generate a new rune-based credential.
Optional
.I restriction
arguments are forwarded to constrain the rune's permissions.
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"rune":..., "unique_id":...}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-macaroon-info (1),
.BR lightning-daemon (1)
